Car controller package

Original: Arcade Car Controller (Lite version) by Perfect Games
Modified by Unlucky Duck

How to use ========================================================================================
Drag car (SunLineGTE) into the scene
Drag FXController (FXController > FXController) into scene

Attach SmoothFollow to camera and set the target to the car to have camera follow car.


Controls ========================================================================================
Car will automatically accelerate
Steer by pressing on screen and moving cursor left and right.
    - left of screen = max left turn
    - right of screen = max right turn
